OL,3,CConcern over 'unsafe workloads' raised
OL,4,Cahead of police service reforms
OL,6,FPolicing requires "pay, training, time
OL,7,Fand support", the body which
OL,8,Frepresents rank-and-file bobbies has
OL,9,Fsaid in response to Home Office
OL,10,Freforms which include introducing a
OL,11,Fnew licence officers will need to do
OL,12,Ftheir job.
OL,14,FPolice officers in England and Wales
OL,15,Fwill be required to hold and renew a
OL,16,Flicence to ensure they "stay at the
OL,17,Ftop of their game" as criminal
OL,18,Ftechniques evolve, the Home Office
OL,19,Fsaid on Saturday.
