OL,3,CConcern over 'unsafe workloads' raised
OL,4,Cahead of police service reforms
OL,6,FThe licensing scheme, along with
OL,7,Fchanges which will allow forces to
OL,8,Frecruit senior leaders from outside
OL,9,Fpolicing, are among the latest reforms
OL,10,Fset to be unveiled by Home Secretary
OL,11,FShabana Mahmood.
OL,13,FThe changes will form part of what the
OL,14,Fgovernment has said will be the police
OL,15,Fservice's largest shake-up since it
OL,16,Fwas founded around 200 years ago.
