OL,3,CConcern over 'unsafe workloads' raised
OL,4,Cahead of police service reforms
OL,6,FUnder the plans, police officers will
OL,7,Fbe required to demonstrate they "have
OL,8,Fthe skills needed to fight crime",
OL,9,Fwith those who repeatedly fall below
OL,10,Fthe required standard, sacked.
OL,12,FThe training programme will set "clear
OL,13,Fstandards" in areas including violence
OL,14,Fagainst women and girls and
OL,15,Fneighbourhood policing, and leadership
OL,16,Fexpectations for staff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
