OL,3,CConcern over 'unsafe workloads' raised
OL,4,Cahead of police service reforms
OL,6,FCrime and policing minister Sarah
OL,7,FJones said: "Every police officer
OL,8,Fneeds to remain match-fit to protect
OL,9,Ftheir communities. As crime evolves,
OL,10,Fwe expect police to evolve more
OL,11,Fquickly.
OL,13,F"The Licence to Practise will equip
OL,14,Fevery officer with the skills and
OL,15,Fcapabilities to do the job - whether
OL,16,Fnew to the force or a policing
OL,17,Fveteran."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
