OL,11,FHowever, the plans have drawn
OL,12,Fcriticism from the Police Federation
OL,13,Fof England and Wales, which said
OL,14,Fofficers are routinely pulled off
OL,15,Fmandatory trainings and burdened with
OL,16,Funsafe workloads.
OL,18,FA spokeswoman for the organisation
OL,19,Fsaid: "Everyone wants professional
OL,20,Fpolicing, but that requires pay,
OL,21,Ftraining, time and support.
