OL,3,CConcern over 'unsafe workloads' raised
OL,4,Cahead of police service reforms
OL,6,F"Officers are routinely pulled off
OL,7,Fmandatory training to plug gaps, work
OL,8,Frest days to stay afloat, and carry
OL,9,Fworkloads no-one would call safe.
OL,11,F"We will await the detail of the white
OL,12,Fpaper but these issues need to be
OL,13,Ffixed."
OL,15,FAlso among the new measures are plans
OL,16,Ffor a graduate recruitment drive, with
OL,17,F#7 million promised to attract
OL,18,Fstudents into graduate neighbourhood
OL,19,Fpolice officer roles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
