OL,3,CConcern over 'unsafe workloads' raised
OL,4,Cahead of police service reforms
OL,6,FIn a bid to boost wellbeing, trauma
OL,7,Ftacker software and a mental health
OL,8,Fcrisis line will be rolled out for
OL,9,Fofficers and staff, while those in
OL,10,Ffront-facing and high-risk roles will
OL,11,Fbe offered yearly psychological risk
OL,12,Fscreenings.
OL,14,FMahmood is expected to outline the
OL,15,Fsweeping reforms in the white paper,
OL,16,F"From local To National: A New Model
OL,17,FFor policing", on Monday.
